pulfalight.title: Display folder number ranges at the parent level in addition to the extent note that says however many folders or containers are represented by the parent level

comments.body:
The `extent` element can be calculated, explaining how much material is actually featured within a component. The container might state "box 12-17, 21", or there might be XML links to the dsc[2] elements, and these must be resolved in order to generate the extent statement.

Currently, this is a part of the normalization routine, so if this is retained, then PULFALight should *not* need to compute anything. This is just a smaller problem with the Traject configuration.
